course_description: This course addresses numerous dimensions of wellness including but not limited to: physical, social, and intellectual. This course also focuses on goal setting and habit development specific to each student's individual needs and goals. The goal of this course is for students to explore wellness topics beyond academic success and traditional physical wellness.
